visual.description: The Business performance planning - Matrix Planning visual enables comprehensive write back & planning from Power BI and is part of the Business performance planning platform. An integrated solution for data warehouse automation, business modelling as well as planning & forecasting with connectivity to accounting platforms like Dynamics, SAP, Oracle, Xero, QuickBooks, etc.
